netfilter: nft_payload: incorrect arithmetics when fetching VLAN header bits

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.164 by commit 550efeff989b041f3746118c0ddd863c39ddc1aa, it was introduced in version v5.5 by commit f6ae9f120dada00abfb47313364c35118469455f. For more details please see the references link.
